            "body": "I'm also encountering this issue and I've tried debugging a bit.\n\nvim.diagnostic data is only updated `on_diagnostic` and `on_publish_diagnostic`, `textDocument/didChange` is triggered but since there's no changes lua_ls doesn't publish diagnostics, it doesn't support `textDocument/diagnostic` so it doesn't update on every `textDocument/didChange`.\n\nThe diagnostics in `vim.diagnostic` doesn't actually change after formatting. But applying the text edits break the signs and extmarks",
